# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:停止損失，避免進一步虧損（常用於投資或商業活動中）
eng:to stop losses, to avoid further losses (commonly used in investment or business activities)
<eg>
yue:投資者應該在虧損擴大前止蝕。 (zou2 tou2 zhe6 ying4 geou3 zai3 kui1 sun1 faat3 daai6 heung3 zuk6 seot6.)
eng:Investors should cut their losses before the losses expand. [end of text]


